title: Vanuatu
text:
Ripablik blong Vanuatu (Franis: "République de Vanuatu", Inglis: "Republic of Vanuatu") i wan kaontri long <a href="pasifik">pasifik</a> we olgeta i tok tok long <a href="Bislama">Bislama</a>. Ol tu narafala ofisel lanwis blong kantri ia hemi inglis mo franis. I gat klosap 115 aelan lanwis we manples blong Vanuatu i toktok long hem. <a href="Kapital">Kapital</a> blong hem i <a href="Port%20Vila">Port Vila</a>.
Histri.
Pedro Fernández de Quirós i bin kamtru long Vanuatu long 1606. James Cook i bin kamtru long Vanuatu long 1774.
Hemi independent aot blong British mo Franis long 30 July 1980.
Jiografi.
Vanuatu i wan akipilego we i gat 83 smolfala aelan we oli bon blong ol volkeno (65 long ol aelan ia oli gat pipol we i sta liv ia).
Vanuatu i gat 14 aelen we aria blong olgeta i kasem 100km2. Oli Espiritu Santo, Malekula, <a href="Efate">Efate</a>, Erromango, <a href="Ambrym">Ambrym</a>, <a href="Tanna%20aeland">Tanna</a>, <a href="Pentikos">Pentikos</a>, Epi, Ambae/Aoba, Gaua, Vanua Lava, Maewo, Malo mo Aneityum/Anatom. Ples we i mo haeap kasem evri narafala ples i Mt Tabwemasana long Santo, we i kasem 1,879 metres (6,165 ft).
Politik.
Vanuatu i wan palamenteri demokrasi, i gat konstitusen mo wan presiden.
Palamen blong Vanuatu i gat 52 memba.
Malvatu Mauri: Nasonal Kaonsel blong olgeta Jif
Politikol pati blong Vanuatu i:
Populaesen blong Vanuatu.
Long July 2016, populaesen blong Vanuatu i stap araon 277 554. Oli tingting se populaesen long 2020 i mo o less 307 815. Blong olgeta, 98, 5 % i melenesian, mo nara 1,5 %
i Polenesian, waetman (Blong <a href="Ostrelia">Ostrelia</a>, <a href="Niu%20Zilan">Niu Zilan</a> o <a href="Franis">Franis</a>), mo tu i gat sam shinwa.
Nasonal Ekonomi.
Agrikalja.
65 % blong ol man Vanuatu oli planem prodius, olsem kokonas, kava mo kopra.
Oli planem sam blong kaekae mo sam blong salem.
Wota risos.
75 % blong rurol populesen blong yumi tede oli nogat aksess long gud wota yet. Mo aim blong gavman blong tede hemi blong <a href="2015">2015</a> everi man blong Vanuatu oli mas kat aksess finis long gud wota.
Spot.
Ol tufala spot we ol man Vanuatu i stap pleiplei long hemi oltaem hemi i kriket mo futbol. Be wan nogud samting i se 
ol yangfala pikinini blong Vanuatu i nogat fulap janis blong tekem pat long tufala spot ia 
from inogat gudfala okanaesesen aotsed long Efate long ol narafala aelan.
Lanwis.
Nasonal lanwis blong Vanuatu emi <a href="Bislama">Bislama</a>. Ol ofisol lanwis emi Bislama, Franis mo Inglis. Ol lanwis oli yusum insaed long skul emi Franis mo Inglis. Olsem wan fomol lanwis Inglis mo Franis ino save bitim narawan from bae kosem divisen.

title: Kalkot Mataskelekele
text:
Kalkot Mataskelekele (1949) i foma <a href="Hed%20blong%20Stet">Hed blong Stet</a> blong <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a>. Em i <a href="presiden">presiden</a> 16 Ogis 2004-16 Ogis 2009. Pati blong hem i <a href="Vanuaaku%20Pati">Vanuaaku Pati</a>.
Hemi nao Ombudsman long Vanuatu.
linked_text: Kalkot Mataskelekele (1949) i foma Hed blong Stet blong [[Vanuatu]]. Em i presiden 16 Ogis 2004-16 Ogis 2009. Pati blong hem i Vanuaaku Pati. Hemi nao Ombudsman long [[Vanuatu]].

title: Sato Kilman
text:
Sato Kilman (30 disemba 1957, <a href="Malekula">Malekula</a>)
hemi elekted long 2009 olsem Lida blong Opposisen blong <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a> afta ol grup blong Grin mo Namakiaute oli disaed blong ko sapotem hem akensem Maxime Carlot Korman we hemi fel blong jenisim kavman plente taem. Long end blong Novemba 2010, Praem Minista <a href="Edward%20Natapei">Edward Natapei</a> hemi appointem hem olsem Deputy Praem Minista mo Minista blong Tred blong riplesem Ham Lini. Hemi ko insaed olsem presiden blong Alliance blong Vanuatu we hemi kam fes pati long Palemen, wetem 16 Mp aot long 52. <a href="Palamen%20blong%20Vanuatu">Palamen blong Vanuatu</a>.

title: Serge Vohor
text:
Serge Vohor (bon long 1955) i bin Praem Minista blong <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a> tri taem, fastaem long Desemba 1995 cassem Febri 1996, sekond taem long Septemba 1996 cassem March 1998 mo tird taem long Juli cassem Decemba 2004. Bifo, hemi bin Foren Minista.
Hemi presiden blong <a href="UMP">UMP</a>.

title: Bislama
text:
Bislama (<a href="Franis%20lanwis">fr.</a> "Bichelamar") hem wan lanwis we olgeta i stap toktok long hem long <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a>, mo hem nasonal lanwis blong kantri ia. 
Sam toktok.
Bislama hem wan kaen <a href="kriol">kriol</a> we i bon afta taem blong <a href="kolonaesesen">kolonaesesen</a>, sam taem long medel blong <a href="19%20senjuri">19 senjuri</a>. Hem miksimap <a href="Ingglis">Ingglis lanwis</a> wetem sam tokples blong Vanuatu.
Narafala eksempol blong kriol olsem, igat <a href="Pijin%20%28toktok%29">Pijin</a> blong <a href="Solomon%20Aelan">Solomon Aelan</a>, <a href="Tok%20Pisin">Tok Pisin</a> long <a href="Papua%20Niugini">PNG</a>, ale <a href="Torres%20Strait%20Kriol">Torres Strait Kriol</a> long <a href="Kwinsilan">Kwinsilan</a> (<a href="Ostrelia">Ostrelia</a>).
linked_text: Bislama (fr. "Bichelamar") hem wan lanwis we olgeta i stap toktok long hem long [[Vanuatu]], mo hem nasonal lanwis blong kantri ia.  [[Sam]] toktok. Bislama hem wan kaen kriol we i bon afta taem blong kolonaesesen, sam taem long medel blong 19 senjuri. Hem miksimap Ingglis lanwis wetem sam tokples blong Vanuatu. Narafala eksempol blong kriol olsem, igat [[Pijin]] blong [[Solomon Aelan]], [[Tok Pisin]] long PNG, ale Torres Strait Kriol long Kwinsilan ([[Ostrelia]]).

title: Port Vila
text: Port Vila, o jes Vila, hem i kapital blong <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a>. Hem i stap long <a href="Efate">Efate</a> aelan. <a href="Gavman">Gavman</a> blong <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a> i stap long ples ia mo hed blong stet blong <a href="kaontri">kaontri</a> ia i stap long ples ia tu.

title: Kapitol
text: Kapitol blong <a href="kaontri">kaontri</a> i taon we i gat gavman blong hem. Exsampol, kapitol blong <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a> i <a href="Port%20Vila">Port Vila</a> mo kapital blong <a href="Ostrelia">Ostrelia</a> i Canberra.

title: Praem Minista blong Vanuatu
text:
Praem Minista blong Vanuatu em i big man long gavman blong kaontri <a href="Ripablik%20blong%20Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a>.
Fes Praem Minista blong Vanuatu hemi Father <a href="Walter%20Lini">Walter Lini</a>. Hemi ron olsem Praem Minista 1980 go kasem 1991.
Tede Praem Minista i <a href="Charlot%20Salwai%20Tabimasma">Charlot Salwai Tabimasma</a> (2019).
linked_text: Praem Minista blong Vanuatu em i big man long gavman blong kaontri [[Vanuatu]]. Fes Praem Minista blong Vanuatu hemi Father [[Walter Lini]]. Hemi ron olsem Praem Minista 1980 go kasem 1991. Tede Praem Minista i Charlot Salwai Tabimasma (2019).

title: Yumi, Yumi, Yumi
text:

title: Ambae Aelan
text:
Ambae Aelan o Aoba hem i wan blong olgeta <a href="aelan">aelan</a> long <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a>. Hem i stap long <a href="Penama">Penama</a> provens, klosap long Santo, <a href="Pentecost">Pentecost</a>, mo Maewo aelan. Ol man eria blong Ambae oli: <a href="Walaha">Walaha</a>, <a href="Nduindui">Nduindui</a>, <a href="Redcliff">Redcliff</a>, <a href="Vingualato">Vingualato</a>, <a href="Lombaha">Lombaha</a>, mo Longana. Provinsial senta blong Penama provens i stap long <a href="Saratamata">Saratamata</a> long is Ambae.
Hem i stap long not pat blong kaontri ia. Long medel long aelan ia, i kat wan bigfala wota i stap. Hem i stap raet antap long hill long medel blong aelan ia. Sapos yu sam taem blong go luk, bambae u sapraes long hem. Yu ting se yu stap long <a href="solwota">solwota</a>. From hem i bigfala wota tumas yu no bilivim se i stap long medel blong wan aelan.
linked_text: Ambae Aelan o Aoba hem i wan blong olgeta aelan long [[Vanuatu]]. Hem i stap long [[Penama]] provens, klosap long Santo, Pentecost, mo Maewo aelan. Ol man eria blong Ambae oli: Walaha, Nduindui, Redcliff, Vingualato, Lombaha, mo Longana. Provinsial senta blong Penama provens i stap long [[Saratamata]] long is Ambae. Hem i stap long not pat blong kaontri ia. Long medel long aelan ia, i kat wan bigfala wota i stap. Hem i stap raet antap long hill long medel blong aelan ia. Sapos yu sam taem blong go luk, bambae u sapraes long hem. Yu ting se yu stap long [[solwota]]. From hem i bigfala wota tumas yu no bilivim se i stap long medel blong wan aelan.

title: Eric A. Havelock
text: Eric Alfred Havelock (Jun 3, 1903 – Epril 4, 1988) emi bin wan classisist long Ingland. Emi bin stap long <a href="Canada">Canada</a> mo long <a href="Unaeted%20Steit">Unaeted Steit</a>. Emi bin wan profesa long Univesiti blong Toronto, mo emi bin jeaman blong depatmen blong classik blong Harvard mo Yale.

title: Robert Gates

title: Spen
linked_text: Spen, o Spein (toktok Spen: "España") i wan kaontri long saotwes blong [[Yurop]]. Spen i wan memba blong Yunion blong Yurop mo NATO. Gavman i monarchy blong parlamen. I saot long [[Franis]] mo [[Andorra]] mo is long [[Portugal]]. Kapitol blong hem i [[Madrid]]. Long 2016, populaesen blong [[Spen]] i stap araon 46 milien.

title: Kurów
text:

Long yia 1939, ol plen blong <a href="Jemani">Jemani</a> bin bonem Kurów long <a href="Wol%20Wo%20Tu">Wol Wo Tu</a>.

title: Tok Pisin
text:

Hemi wan frend blong <a href="Bislama">Bislama</a>. Sapos yu toktok Bislama long wan man blong Papua Niugini bambae hemi kasem.

title: Kokonas
text:
Kokonas ("Cocos nucifera") hem wan kaen <a href="pamtri">pamtri</a> we istap gru long <a href="tropikol%20eria">tropikol eria</a> blong wol, long so klosap blo solwora. Hemi stap olbaot long <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a> tu.
Hao man i yusum.
Trink.
Taem fresh kokonas hemi grin kala, hemi fit blong trink. Bislama i kolem “<a href="navara">navara</a>”, igat spesel nem bl'm long ol lanwis Vanuatu. 
Man o pikinini i klaem antap long stamba blong kokonas, holem kokonas, tanem, tekem. Katem hol wetem naef, ale trink. Wora bl'm i swit.
Kakae.
Fresh kokonas igat <a href="palp">palp</a> bl'm we man isave kakae, we hem swit tu.
Ale spos kokonas i raep moa, palp ia bae i kam strong, hem had tumas blong kakae wetem tut. Be hemia man i save skrasem nao: long kastom oli skrasem wetem <a href="kokiyas">kokiyas</a>; tedei wetem wan spesel kaen metal bled.
Skrasem gogo, yu tekem kokonas ia mo skwisim wetem tufala han, mekem "melek blong kokonas". Oli melekem kakae olsemia long <a href="laplap">laplap</a>. 
Kopra.
Mit blong kokonas oli mekem oel blong <a href="kopra">kopra</a> long hem, yusum blong mekem sop o shampu o wanem. Hemia bigfela pat blong <a href="exportation">exportation</a> blong Vanuatu.
Sel kokonas.
Taem skrasem kokonas finis, man i save sakemaot sel bl'm, o i save yusum bakegen. 
Wan yus bl'm hem olsem wan <a href="glas">glas</a> blong trink <a href="kava">kava</a> l'm.
Lif kokonas.
Ol lif kokonas igat plante yus bl'm. Espeseli oli wivim <a href="mat">mat</a> l'm, spesol mat blong lif-kokonas, blong staon l'm long graon.
Yumi save wivim defren kaen <a href="basket">basket</a> tu; mo ol pleple blo pikinini tu.

Taem fresh kokonas hemi grin kala, hemi fit blong trink. Bislama i kolem “[[navara]]”, igat spesel nem bl'm long ol lanwis Vanuatu.  [[Man]] o pikinini i klaem antap long stamba blong kokonas, holem kokonas, tanem, tekem. [[Katem]] hol wetem naef, ale trink. Wora bl'm i swit. Kakae. Fresh kokonas igat palp bl'm we man isave kakae, we hem swit tu. Ale spos kokonas i raep moa, palp ia bae i kam strong, hem had tumas blong kakae wetem tut. Be hemia man i save skrasem nao: long kastom oli skrasem wetem kokiyas; tedei wetem wan spesel kaen metal bled. Skrasem gogo, yu tekem kokonas ia mo skwisim wetem tufala han, mekem "melek blong kokonas". Oli melekem kakae olsemia long [[laplap]].  Kopra. Mit blong kokonas oli mekem oel blong kopra long hem, yusum blong mekem sop o shampu o wanem. Hemia bigfela pat blong exportation blong Vanuatu. Sel kokonas. Espeseli oli wivim mat l'm, spesol mat blong lif-kokonas, blong staon l'm long graon. Yumi save wivim defren kaen basket tu; mo ol pleple blo pikinini tu.

title: Kanada
text:
Kanada i wan kaontri blong <a href="Not%20Amerika">Not Amerika</a>. Hemi closup long Amerika nomo. Hemi wan federasen witem ten provinses mo tri teritori. Hemi wan membe blong Kommonwelt mo kween blong Canada hemi <a href="Matthew%20Thompson">Matthew Thompson</a> blong Inglan. Kapital blong hem i <a href="Otawa">Otawa</a>.
Praem Minista: Justin Trudeau.

title: Islam
text: Islam i wan rilijin. I gat fulup man long <a href="Esia">Esia</a> mo <a href="Afrika">Afrika</a> we oli Muslim. Muslim meanem se man blong Islam. Man we hemi bin mekem Islam, nem blong hem <a href="Muhammed">Muhammed</a>.

title: Muhammed
text:
Muhammed i holiman blong <a href="Islam">Islam</a>. Muhammed no i <a href="God">God</a>.
Hem i bin bon long 570 A.D. long <a href="Mecca">Mecca</a>. Hem i bin lusum papa mo mama taem hem i smol. Hem i bin laef olsem ol pua. Hem i bin winim wan gud nem olsem wan man blong mekem pis. Hem i bin mared taem hem i bin gat 25 yia. Long 610, hem i bin prea mo hem i bin tingting hevi long Maont Hira. Hem i bin talem se enjel Gabriel i bin kamaot long hem mo i bin givim hem wan mesej we i kam long Allah (<a href="God">God</a>). Hem i klemem se hem i kasem toktok we i kam long God tru long Gabriel stat long 620 i go kasem 632. Ol komiunikesen ia, we ol disaepol blong hem oli stap talem baehat, oli bin raetem afta insaed long <a href="Koran">Koran</a>, tabu buk blong Islam.

Ol komiunikesen ia, we ol disaepol blong hem oli stap talem baehat, oli bin raetem afta insaed long Koran, tabu buk blong Islam.

title: Wol Wo Tu
text: Wol Wo Tu hemi wan bigfala wo we hemi tek ples long 1939 kasem 1945 bitwin ol Allis (<a href="Unaeted%20Kingdom">Inglan</a>, <a href="Yunaeted%20Stet%20blong%20Amerika">Amerika</a>, <a href="USSR">USSR</a>, <a href="Jaena">Jaena</a> mo ol fren blong trifala) mo Aksis (<a href="Jemani">Jemani</a>, <a href="Japan">Japan</a> mo ol fren blong tufala).

title: Buk Blong Momon
linked_text: <ns>0</ns>  <revision></revision>  <parentid>31991</parentid>  <timestamp>2018-12-18T01:39:23Z</timestamp>  <contributor></contributor>  <username>Underneaththesun</username>    <model>wikitext</model>  <format>text/x-wiki</format> Buk blong Momon: Wan Narafala Testeman blong [[Jisas Kraes]] Wan mesenja blong heven we nem blong hem [[Moronae]] i lidim [[Josef Smit]] long wan hil we ol gol plet i bin stap slip haed blong plante senturi. Ol gol plet ia oli tekem ol raeting blong ol profet we oli talemaot stori blong wanem we God i bin mekem wetem ol fas man we i bin stap long [[Amerika]]. Josef Smit i bin transletem wanem i bin stap insaed long ol plet ia tru long paoa blong God. Ol profet insaed long Buk blong Momon oli bin save abaot misin blong Sevya mo oli bin tijim gospel blong Hem. Taem Hem i laef bakegen long ded, Kraes i bin kamaot long ol pipol ia. Hem i bin tijim olgeta gospel blong Hem mo Hem i bin stanemap Jos blong Hem. Buk blong Momon i pruvum se God i toktok long man mo i stap singaotem olgeta blong mekem tabu wok blong hem long taem tedei mo jeneresen ia semmak olsem wetem ol jeneresen bifo. Presiden Ezra Taft Benson i bin talem se Buk blong Momon i ki ston long trifala wei: Buk blong [[Momon]] i Testefae abaot Kraes. Wan stamba tingting blong Buk blong Momon i blong mekem tingting blong ol pipol i [[kam]] strong se [[Jisas]] Hem i Kraes.

title: Ostrelia
text:
Ostrelia i wan <a href="kaontri">kaontri</a> long <a href="Pasifik">Pasifik</a> we olgeta save tok tok long <a href="Inglis">Inglis</a>. <a href="Kapitol">Kapitol</a> blong hem i <a href="Canberra">Canberra</a>. Praem minister blong Ostrelia hemi <a href="Scott%20Morrison">Scott Morrison</a> (2015). Kween blong Ostrelia hemi <a href="Elisabet%20II">Elisabet II</a>. England i bin bonem Ostrelia long 1788, taem olgeta i putum sum prisonas blong hem long <a href="Niu%20Saot%20Waels">Niu Saot Waels</a>.
Ostrelia i gat sikis stet mo tri teritori we oli stap long maenlan. I gat tu ol teritori long afsaed maenlan blong Ostrelia, <a href="Krismas%20Ailan">Krismas Ailan</a> hemi wan eksampol.

title: Papua Niugini
text: Independen Stet bilong Papua Niugini i <a href="kaontri">kaontri</a> long <a href="Pasifik">Pasifik</a> we olgeta oli save tok tok long <a href="English">Inglis</a> mo <a href="Tok%20Pisin">Tok Pisin</a> mo <a href="Hiri%20Motu">Hiri Motu</a>. Olgeta oli gat 850 lanwis we manples blong Papua Niugini i toktok oltaem. <a href="Kapital">Kapital</a> blong hem i <a href="Port%20Moresby">Port Moresby</a>. Praem minista blong Papua Niugini hemi <a href="Michael%20Somare">Michael Somare</a>. Kween blong Papua Niugini hemi <a href="Elisabet%20II">Elisabet II</a>. Hemi independent aot long <a href="Ostrelia">Ostrelia</a> long 1975. Populaesen blong hem i baot 7 milien.
linked_text: Independen Stet bilong Papua Niugini i [[kaontri]] long [[Pasifik]] we olgeta oli save tok tok long [[Inglis]] mo [[Tok Pisin]] mo Hiri Motu. Olgeta oli gat 850 lanwis we manples blong Papua Niugini i toktok oltaem. Kapital blong hem i Port Moresby. Praem minista blong Papua Niugini hemi [[Michael Somare]]. Kween blong Papua Niugini hemi [[Elisabet II]]. Hemi independent aot long [[Ostrelia]] long 1975. Populaesen blong hem i baot 7 milien.

title: Tru Jisas Jioj
text:
Tru Jisas Jioj i indipenden jioj wes setemap i <a href="Beijing">Beijing</a>, <a href="Jaena">Jaena</a> i 1917. Tede, mo 2.5 milian memba i fotifaef kaontri mo sikis kontinen. jioj blo <a href="Pentekos">Pentekos</a> grup blong Kristen hemi fomemap i eli twante senturi. Jioj bilivim Jisas-nem. Jioj aim mo prij gospel tu evri neson bifo seken kam blong Jisas.

title: Jemani

title: Yunaeted Stet blong Amerika
text:
Yunaeted Stet i wan kaontri blong <a href="Not%20Amerika">Not Amerika</a>. Hemi wan federasen we i gat wan konstitusen, witem 50 stet. 48 stet blong em ol i closup long <a href="Kanada">Kanada</a> mo <a href="Mexico">Mexico</a> nomo. Wan stet nem <a href="Alaska">Alaska</a> i stap long notwes kona blong Not Amerika. Alaska i klosap long Kanada long is saed mo long Bering Strait long wes saed. Wan stet nem <a href="Hawaii">Hawaii</a> i stap long <a href="Pasifik">Pasifik</a>; em i gat plante aelan nomo.
Kapital blong Yunaeted Stet i <a href="Washington%2C%20D.C.">Washington, D.C.</a>.
Presidens blong hem i <a href="Joe%20Biden">Joe Biden</a>.
Long 2019, populesen blong Yunaeted Stet i stap aroun 328,239,523.
Gavman blong Yunaeted Stet blong Amerika i gat trifala pat: executive branch, legislative branch, mo judicial branch. Executive Branch em i enfosem ol law. Legislative branch em i mekem ol law. Judicial branch em i interpretem ol law.
Yunaeted Stet em i independent aot long British long 4 Julae 1776.

Wan stet nem [[Alaska]] i stap long notwes kona blong Not Amerika. Alaska i klosap long Kanada long is saed mo long Bering Strait long wes saed. Wan stet nem [[Hawaii]] i stap long [[Pasifik]]; em i gat plante aelan nomo. Kapital blong Yunaeted Stet i Washington, D.C.. Presidens blong hem i [[Joe Biden]]. Long 2019, populesen blong [[Yunaeted Stet]] i stap aroun 328,239,523. Gavman blong [[Yunaeted Stet blong Amerika]] i gat trifala pat: executive branch, legislative branch, mo judicial branch. Executive Branch em i enfosem ol law. Legislative branch em i mekem ol law. Judicial branch em i interpretem ol law. [[Yunaeted Stet]] em i [[independent]] aot long British long 4 Julae 1776.

title: Josef Smit
text:
Josef Smit (Sharon, <a href="Vermont">Vermont</a>, <a href="1805">1805</a>-Carthage, <a href="Illinois">Illinois</a>, <a href="1844">1844</a>) i bin laef long <a href="Yunaeted%20Stet">Yunaeted Stet</a>, we hem i wan kantri ia nomo we i bin stap gat fridom blong relijin long taem ia. Hem i bin wan taem we relijin i impoten tumas long Is
pat blong Yunaeted Stet. Ol famle memba blong hem oli bin stap insaed long relijin mo oli bin stap lukaotem trutok oltaem. Be plante minista oli bin klemem se oli bin gat tru gospel.
Josef i bin wantem blong save wijwan long ol grup blong relijin ia i stret (Joseph Smith—History 1:18). Baebol i bin tijim se i gat “wan Masta nomo, wan tok nomo blong bilif long hem, mo wan baptaes nomo” (Efesas 4:5). Josef i bin go long ol defren jos, be tingting blong
hem i bin stap fasfas yet we wijwan jos hem i mas joenem.

Hem i bin wan taem we relijin i impoten tumas long Is pat blong [[Yunaeted Stet]]. Ol famle memba blong hem [[oli]] bin stap insaed long relijin mo [[oli]] bin stap lukaotem trutok oltaem. [[Be]] plante minista oli bin klemem se oli bin gat tru gospel. Josef i bin wantem blong save wijwan long ol grup blong relijin ia i stret (Joseph Smith—History 1:18). Baebol i bin tijim se i gat “wan Masta nomo, wan tok nomo blong bilif long hem, mo wan baptaes nomo” ([[Efesas]] 4:5). Josef i bin go long ol defren jos, be tingting blong hem i bin stap fasfas yet we wijwan jos hem i mas joenem.

title: God
text:
God i Nambawan Deiti blong staka <a href="rilijin">rilijin</a>. Hem i Papa blong pipol long Heven.
God blong <a href="Kristaniti">Kristaniti</a>.
God blong Kristaniti i lavem pipol. Hem i krae wetem pipol taem pipol stap safa mo hem i stap glad taem ol biliva mekem wanem we hem i raet. Hem i gat bigfala powa, mo hem i mekem wol, mo hem i gud tumas.
God hem i mekem wol mo i mekem ol pipol blong oli stap wetem hem mo oli wosipim hem. Be ol pipol evriwan oli mekem i nogud ale oli nomo save stap wetem hem fromwe hem i tabu tumas mo oli stap mekem i nogud. Be hem i lavem ol pipol mo i senem pikini blong hem Jisas blong hem i ded long kros mo hem i tekem panismen blong ol pipol. Ale ol pipol, sipos oli wantem kam stap wetem God, mo oli bilif long hem, oli save kam stap wetem God, mo oli kam ol pikinini blong hem. Mo wan dei God bambae i mekem wan nufala wol we evri samting i gud mo bambae hem i tekem ol pipol we ol i bilif long hem bae oli kam stap wetem hem long nufala wol we i gud tumas.
Papa long Heven i Givimaot Gospel blong Hem long Evri Dispensesen. Wan impoten wei we God i soemaot lav blong Hem long pipol i taem Hem i singaotem ol profet, we oli kasem prishud—paoa mo raet we oli givim long man blong mekem samting long nem blong God blong ol pikinini blong Hem oli save stap sef.

title: John Wycliffe
text: I bon long nambafotin senturi long <a href="Inglan">Inglan</a>. Man blong skul long teoloji long Yunivesiti blong Oksfod. Hem i bin tijim se Katolik Jos i no bin gat ol prishud ki, se Tabu Komunion (o sakramen) i no stret bodi blong Kraes, mo se jos i no mas gat paoa blong politik ova long ol pipol. Hem i bin transletem <a href="Baebol">Baebol</a> i kam long <a href="Inglis">Inglis</a>. Hem i ded long 31 Disemba 1384.

title: Martin Luther
text:
Hem i bin bon long 10 Novemba 1483, long <a href="Jemani">Jemani</a>.
Hem i bin stadi long Yunivesiti blong Erfurt mo Witenbeg. Hem i bin nilim 95 stadi we hem i bin raetem long doa blong Kasel Jos blong toktok agensem plante tijing we i stap abaot <a href="Roman%20Katolik%20Jos">Roman Katolik Jos</a>, mo hemia i tekem tu praktis blong mekem ol pipol oli pem mane blong mekem se oli kam klin long ol sin blong olgeta. Hem i bin ded long 18 Febwari 1546.

title: William Tyndale
text: William Tyndale hem i bin bon long <a href="Wales">Wales</a> long 1494. Hem i bin stadi long <a href="Oksfod">Oksfod</a> mo long <a href="Cambridge">Cambridge</a>. Hem i bin transletem <a href="Niu%20Testeman">Niu Testeman</a> i kam long <a href="Inglis">Inglis</a>. Hem i bin mekem se ol pipol olbaot oli save gat raet blong ridim ol skripja blong hemia i talemaot ol giaman doktrin mo ol korapsen blong ol lida blong <a href="relijin">relijin</a>. Oli bin kilimded hem long 6 Oktoba 1536.

title: John Calvin
text: Hem i bin bon long 10 Julae 1509, long <a href="Franis">Franis</a>. Hem i stadi long <a href="Paris">Paris</a> blong hem i kam wan pris. Hem i bin wan bigfala lida long ol muvmen blong mekemgud <a href="Katolik%20Jos">Katolik Jos</a>. Hem i bin laef plante taem blong laef blong hem long <a href="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>. Hem i bin tijim se man nomo oli nating mo sore blong <a href="God">God</a> nomo i save sevem olgeta. Hem i bin raetem plante tingting blong hem long saed blong <a href="Baebol">Baebol</a>. Hem i bin ded long 27 Mei 1564.

title: Buddha
text: Hem i bin bon long 563 B.K. long wan laen blong Jif long <a href="Nepal">Nepal</a>. Hem i bin wari long ol safaring raon long hem. Hem i ronwe long rij haos blong papa blong hem, i lego wol ia, mo i laef olsem ol pua man. Hem i bin lukaotem blong kasem moa laet, hem i bin faenem wanem we hem i singaotem “rod blong kam fri.” Hem i klem se hem i bin kasem Nirvana, wan ples we oli fogetem ol samting, ol soa long bodi, o wol ia. Hem i kam wan tija blong wan komuniti blong ol monk.

title: Confucius
text: Confucius i bon long 551 B.K. Hem i no bin gat papa o mama taem hem i pikinini. Hem i fas top tija blong yunivesiti long <a href="Jaena">Jaena</a>. Hem i man blong Jaena i save gat ol gud tingting long saed blong fasin blong man. Hem i no bin talem plante samting long saed blong man blong spirit o paoa we i hae. Hem i bin biliv se heven i bin givim hem wan tabu misin olsem jampion blong gud mo samting we i tru.

title: Tabu Spirit
text:
Tabu Spirit i nambatri memba blong Godhed. Hem i wan man we
i spirit mo Hem i no gat wan bodi blong mit mo bun. Tabu Spirit i testefae abaot trutok.
Ol Presen blong Spirit.
Ol presen blong Spirit oli ol spesel blesing blong spirit we Lod i givim 
long wanwan we i klin inaf blong hem i yusum blong gud blong hem mo blong olgeta oli yusum tu blong blesem ol narawan.

title: St Peter's College (Auckland)
text: St Peter's College, Auckland hemi wan big fala secondri skul blong Katolic we olgeta Boe nao oli stap go stadi long hem long sentral <a href="Auckland">Auckland</a> long <a href="Niu%20Zilan">Niu Zilan</a>. Olgeta Christian Brothers nao oli statem skul ia long yia 1939 be long 2008, skul ia hemi emploem olgeta full taem wokas blong woka long hem. Skul ia hemi karem maximum multi-ethnic roll blong 1,200 studens. Long saed blong olgeta academic, skul hemi offerem olgeta high level qualificason olsem Nasonal Certificat blong Educasonal Achivment (NCEA) assesmen system wetem Cambrige Internasonal Examinason (CIE). Skul hemi save enrollem 70 internasonal studens stret long wan taem.

title: Kiai (lanwis)
text:
Kiai (Fortsenal, Vorozenale) hem wan lanwis blong <a href="Vanuatu">Ripablik blong Vanuatu</a>.
Stamba ples blong hem, vilej blong "Fortsenal" long <a href="Santo%20aelan">Santo aelan</a> (<a href="Sanma">Sanma provens</a>).
Histri blong lanwis ia.
Olsem evri <a href="Lanwis%20blong%20Vanuatu">tokples blong Vanuatu</a>, Kiai hem wan <a href="Oceanic%20lanwis">Oceanic lanwis</a>, memba blong bigfela <a href="Austronesian%20lanwis">Austronesian famle</a>.
Lanwis ia tedei.
Tedei ia, ol lingwis i talem se igat 450 man i stap yet we i save tok long lanwis blong Kiai.
linked_text: Kiai (Fortsenal, Vorozenale) hem wan lanwis blong Ripablik blong Vanuatu. Stamba ples blong hem, vilej blong "Fortsenal" long [[Santo aelan]] (Sanma provens). Histri blong lanwis ia. Olsem evri tokples blong Vanuatu, Kiai hem wan Oceanic lanwis, memba blong bigfela Austronesian famle. Lanwis ia tedei. Tedei ia, ol lingwis i talem se igat 450 man i stap yet we i save tok long lanwis blong Kiai.

title: Latvia
text:
Latvia (lv. - "Latvia, Latvijas Republika") i kaontri long <a href="Europe">Europe</a>. I long <a href="Estonia">Estonia</a>, <a href="Rusia">Rusia</a>, <a href="Belarus">Belarus</a>, <a href="Litwania">Litwania</a>. Kapital blong hem i <a href="Riga">Riga</a>. Presidens blong hem i <a href="Egils%20Levits">Egils Levits</a>. Praem Minista blong hem i <a href="Arturs%20Kri%C5%A1j%C4%81nis%20Kari%C5%86%C5%A1">Arturs Krišjānis Kariņš</a> (2020). Eria i 64 589 km2.
Latvia hemi independent aot blong Rusia long 18 Novemba 1918 (1918-1940) mo blong <a href="YSSR">YSSR</a> long 21 Ogis 1991.
Populaesen blong Latvia.
Long Jenuware 2018, populaesen blong Latvia i stap araon 1,934,379. Blong olgeta, 62,2 % i Latvian, mo 25,2 % i Rusian.
Lanwis.
Nasonal lanwis blong Latvia emi Latvian.
Gavman.
Latvia i wan palamenteri demokrasi, i gat konstitusen mo wan presiden.
Gavman blong Latvia i gat trifala pat: executive branch, legislative branch, mo judicial branch. Executive branch em i enfosem ol law. Legislative branch em i mekem ol law. Judicial branch em i interpretem ol law.
Spot.
Latvia i big kaontry long aes hokey. Staka pipol plei basketbol mo floabol.

title: Auckland Grammar School
text:
Auckland Grammar School, hemi wan bigfala <a href="sekondri%20skul">sekondri skul</a> oli stap go stadi long hem long sentral <a href="Auckland">Auckland</a> long <a href="Niu%20Zilan">Niu Zilan</a>. Olgeta Sir George Grey nao oli statem skul ia long yia 1868. Skul ia hemi karem roll blong mo o les 2500 studens. Long saed blong olgeta akademik, skul hemi offerem olgeta "high level qualification" olsem assesmen system wetem Cambrige Internasonal Examinason. Skul hemi save enrollem 70-80 internasonal studens stret long wan yia.
Olgeta well-known mo foma graduets long disfala skul hemi inkludim Sir <a href="Edmund%20Hillary">Edmund Hillary</a> (Klaemb bigfala hil) wetem <a href="Russell%20Crowe">Russell Crowe</a>.

I gat plante handred spot we i stap, stat wetem olgeta we i nidim tu man nomo, i go long olgeta we plante handred man i patisipet, maet wetem ol team o oli kompit olsem wanwan man nomo.
Klosap ol man i luksave spot olsem ol aktiviti we yu mas yusum ol skil blong bodi o ol mit blong bodi, wetem ol bigfala kompitesen olsem Olympic Games i biliv ol spot hem i olgeta we folem tingting ia, mo ol narafala oganaesesen olsem Council of Europe i ting spot i olsem ol aktiviti we yu mas yusum bodi. Be, i gat samfala aktiviti we nem blong olgeta hem i ol gem blong maen, we oli kompit be oli no yusum ol bodi blong olgeta. International Olympic Committee i luksave jes mo brij olsem ol ril spot, mo SportAccord, we hem i wan intanasonal spot oganasesen asoseason, i luksave faef defren spot we yu no yusum bodi blo yu, be oli putum namba long olgeta gem blong maen we yu save tekem olsem oli ril spot.
Klosap evritaem spot i gat ol rul o kastom, we i stap blo mekemsua se fasin blong kompit i stret, mo i alao stret jajmen blo hapen lo saed blo huia i winim ol gem. Jajmen long saed blo wijwan man i winim wan gem blong ol spot blong bodi i save kam tru long fasin blong winim ol gol o kasem wan laen bifo long ol narafala man, o tru long jajmen blong ol jaj we oli skelem ol defren kaen eria long pefomans, we i tekem tu jajmen long saed blong olsem teknokol pefomans o ol filing we atist i givim.

title: Pepa
text:
Pepa i wan ting, pipol ol i mekem long fiber long wud mo rags. Pipol i raet long pepa, mekem olgeta buk long pepa. Pepa absorbs wora, pipol i usum pepa blong wasem ol ting.
Pipol i bin mekem pepa fastaem long Jaena long 105 B.K. Long Jaena, pepa i kamtru long India, long Middle East, mo long Itali. Long Inglan i bin mekem wan masin blong mekem pepa before 1812.

title: Pijin
text: Pijin i wan kaen animol. Olgeta pijin ol i gat feda, tu leg, tu wing, mo wan backbone. Olgeta pijin ol i putum egg. Pijin long tede ol i no gat tut. Olgeta pijin ol i gat naem blong Baeoloji blong Aves. <a href="Grin%20pijin">Grin pijin</a>, <a href="dakdak">dakdak</a>, <a href="hoknaet">hoknaet</a>, <a href="sigal">sigal (pijin blong solwota)</a>, <a href="pijin%20blong%20hariken">pijin blong hariken</a>, longfala nek, mo <a href="nalaklak">nalaklak</a> ol i somfala kaen pijin.

title: Mikelanjelo
text: Mikelanjelo (Michelangelo di Lodovico Buonarroti Simoni (6 Maj 1475 – 18 Februari 1564) i wan man blong at blong <a href="Itali">Itali</a> blong Renesans (Renaissance). Hemi bin bon long <a href="Caprese">Caprese</a> long Itali. Papa blong hem i bin wok long gavman blong Chiusa. Chiusa i wan siti blong Itali. Mikelanjelo bin mekem wan bigfala pitja long siling long Sistine Chapel long Rome, mo plante moa pitja. Hemi bin mekem plante skulpja. Nem blong wan skulpja blong hem David, mo nem blong wan moa skulpja blong hem Pieta.

title: Kava
text:
Kava hemi wan plan we i krow long <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a>. Stret nem blong hem hemi "Piper methysticum."
Ol man oli iusum rus blong hem blong mekem wan drink. Ol man mo sam woman tu oli drink kava long sava long wan ples nem blong hem nakamal. Oli servem kava long shell blong kokonas. Kava i mekem se ol man we oli drink oli harem gud long hem.

title: Santo aelan
text:
Santo Aelan hem i wan blong olgeta aelan long Vanuatu. I gat 26 lanwis long Santo. Long aelan ia, i gat <a href="Luganville">Luganville</a>, hem i kapital blong <a href="Sanma">Sanma</a>.
Long Wol wo tu, armi blong Amerika hem i bin kriatem wan stamba. Nem blong stamba hem i Buttons. afta long wol wo tu santo i bin kat fulap development i kam antap mo ol man oli bin save sentem pikinini ko long skul mo kasem gudfala wok mo oli bin jusum lablas olsem wan pablic ples we ol man oli save ko stap togeta long taem blong wan lafet o eni taem we oli wantem seleparsion olsem interdependence day

title: Laplap
text:
Laplap hemi kastom <a href="kakae">kakae</a> blong <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a>. 
Hao blong mekem.
Igat ol defdefren kaen laplap long Vanuatu. Samfala yu tekem <a href="yam">yam</a>, samfala <a href="taro">taro</a>, o <a href="maniok">maniok</a>, o <a href="bresfrut">bresfrut</a>; ale skrasem, skrasem go–go, pushum igo long bigfala lif olsem <a href="lif%20banana">lif banana</a>. Samtaem yu save adem <a href="fis">fis</a> tu, o spos no, mit blong <a href="buluk">buluk</a>, o <a href="pig">pig</a>, o <a href="faol">faol</a> tu.
Ale, skwisim melek blong <a href="kokonas">kokonas</a> igo long hem. 
Kavremap evriwan wetem lif (banana lif o wanem), long smosmol bandel o sipos no long wan bigwan bandel wantaem. Finis ale, putum evriwan long <a href="stonoven">stonoven</a>, hemia oven we istap long graon, kavremap wetem hot ston; bekem. Taem hem tan finis, yu openem oven, tekemaot laplap.
Olgeta yus.
Oli bekem laplap olsemia blong bigfela grup i save sherem: olsem, long wan <a href="lafet">lafet</a> blong vilej, wan <a href="maret">maret</a>, wan <a href="Kastom">kastom seremoni</a>, wan selebresen olsem.
linked_text: Laplap hemi kastom [[kakae]] blong [[Vanuatu]].  Hao blong mekem. Igat ol defdefren kaen laplap long Vanuatu. Samfala yu tekem [[yam]], samfala [[taro]], o [[maniok]], o bresfrut; ale skrasem, skrasem go–go, pushum igo long bigfala lif olsem lif banana. Samtaem yu save adem [[fis]] tu, o spos no, mit blong [[buluk]], o [[pig]], o faol tu. Ale, skwisim melek blong [[kokonas]] igo long hem.  Kavremap evriwan wetem lif (banana lif o wanem), long smosmol bandel o sipos no long wan bigwan bandel wantaem. Finis ale, putum evriwan long stonoven, hemia oven we istap long graon, kavremap wetem hot ston; bekem. Taem hem tan finis, yu openem oven, tekemaot laplap. Olgeta yus. Oli bekem laplap olsemia blong bigfela grup i save sherem: olsem, long wan lafet blong vilej, wan maret, wan kastom seremoni, wan selebresen olsem.

title: Tongoa
text:
Tongoa hemi wan smol aelan blong yumi long <a href="vanuatu">vanuatu</a>.hemi biggest aeland insait long <a href="shepherds%20group">shepherds group</a> blong ol aeland we oli stap insait long Shefa province wan long ol province blong Vanuatu. Long histry blong aelan ia, hemi wan aelan we bifo hem joen tugata wetem, <a href="Tongariri">Tongariri</a>,<a href="%20Buninga"> Buninga</a>,<a href="%20Valea"> Valea</a>, <a href="Ewose">Ewose</a>,<a href="%20Laika"> Laika</a> mo <a href="Tevala">Tevala</a> mo ful nem blong olgeta aelan ia long taem bifo hemi <a href="Kuwa%C3%A9">Kuwaé</a>.
Samples long 1400 wan kastom erapsem I prokem mo sepereitem olgeta aelan ia.
Ol pipol blong Tongoa oli toktok 2 langwitsh. Nem blong tufala langwitsh ia hemi Namakura mo Nakanamanga. Tongoa i gad 14 Vilij. Long saotsaot west to notnot is sait blong aeland I gad <a href="Meriu">Meriu</a>, <a href="Bongabonga">Bongabonga</a>, <a href="Mangarisu">Mangarisu</a>, <a href="Euta">Euta</a>, <a href="Itakoma">Itakoma</a>mo <a href="Matangi">Matangi</a> we oli toktok <a href="Namakura">Namakura</a> mo long notnott is to saotsaot west sait I gad <a href="Panita">Panita</a>, <a href="Lumbukiti">Lumbukiti</a>, <a href="Ravenga">Ravenga</a>, <a href="Lupalea">Lupalea</a>, <a href="Pele">Pele</a>, <a href="Purao">Purao</a> mo <a href="Kurumambe">Kurumambe</a> we oli toktok <a href="Nakanamanga">Nakanamanga</a>.
linked_text: Tongoa hemi wan smol aelan blong yumi long [[vanuatu]].hemi biggest aeland insait long shepherds group blong ol aeland we oli stap insait long Shefa province wan long ol province blong Vanuatu. Long histry blong aelan ia, hemi wan aelan we bifo hem joen tugata wetem, Tongariri, Buninga, Valea, Ewose, Laika mo Tevala mo ful nem blong olgeta aelan ia long taem bifo hemi Kuwaé. Samples long 1400 wan kastom erapsem I prokem mo sepereitem olgeta aelan ia. Ol pipol blong Tongoa oli toktok 2 langwitsh. Nem blong tufala langwitsh ia hemi Namakura mo Nakanamanga. Tongoa i gad 14 Vilij. Long saotsaot west to notnot is sait blong aeland I gad Meriu, Bongabonga, [[Mangarisu]], Euta, Itakomamo Matangi we oli toktok [[Namakura]] mo long notnott is to saotsaot west sait I gad Panita, Lumbukiti, Ravenga, Lupalea, Pele, Purao mo Kurumambe we oli toktok Nakanamanga.

taem yumi go long nara aelan mbae yumi mas crosem solwota long sip o plen.

title: Matarine
text:
Matarine, o madarine, o mandrin, hem i wan <a href="frut">frut</a> we pipol likem kakae. Ol matarine gat yelo o orenj frutskin mo swit orenj palp.
Matarine i gro long smol matarine <a href="tri">tri</a> blong species wetem nem long toktok Latin "<a href="Citrus%20reticulata">Citrus reticulata</a>". Netif lan blong matarine tri i <a href="Is%20Esia">Is Esia</a>.
Long <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a> mifala i gat wan spesel aelan we ol matarine i fulap long hem, hemi collem <a href="Aniwa">Aniwa</a>.

title: Tanna soup
text:
Tanna sup hemi wan kakae we hem i kam aut long sauten island blo Vanuatu we oli kolem Tanna, fulap lo ol aeland blo Vanuatu tete tu oli stap atoptem kaen stael blo kook ia. Tanna sup hemi geak ; from hemi savem taem. Fulap lo ol man tete long Vanuatu oli traem blo atem ap ol different kind stael long kaen kaekae ia tu.
Tanna sup hemi main kaekae blo ol man Tanna , hemi queak mo easi blo kook afta we ol man or woman long vilage oli kam long karen. kaen kaekae ia hemi includum ani enegi kakae olsem : manioc, taro , yam, mo fulap more...ol protective kakae olsem island kabbage , wite boon, soshoot, mo fulap more...meat blo hem olsem puluk, nani got, fish more fulap mo. Tanna sup i kud from hem i combinem tri kind kakae wantaem olem ; bodi building kakae, energy kakae mo prodective kakae long same taem. Stadi i sowem se Tanna sup hemi kilim nintypercent blo sick inside long bodi.Blo ademup, Tanna sup hemi save cosem sick tu sapose yu no folem gud wei blo kook blo hem. Tumas cress blo puluk or fish or melek blo kokonut i save makem pel i ron.
Bae fulap island pae oli save atem ol style long kaen kakae ia hamas, be name Tanna sup hemi still stap yet, pae ol man save changem sweatness hamas be name i still stap sa mak. Blo endem smol lukluk abautem Tanna sup , Tanna sup hemi wan gud kakae i save helpem man o woman long side blo haelt, grouth blo wan bikinini mo life expectancy blo wan man. Be tanna sup hemi still kohed yet long ol island blo Vanuatu.

title: Susut
text:
Susut hem wan vejetebol wei i koro lo buss olsem rop yu save kakae fruit blo hem mo ol top blo leave blo hem tu. 
Mo tu yu save koku susut fruit mo top blo leave wetem wan gudfala met blo yu wetem famli blo yu.

title: Coconut
text: Coconut tri hemi wan veri gud tri, hemi kat fulap use blo hem. Hemi wan tri we yu save usum blo kakae, fitim ol animal blo yu wetem olsem : big, faul, pusikat, mo fulap mo animal. oli save makem hause wetem lif blo hem, mat blo staon, basket blo kakae .Blo ademup , coconut oli makem copra lo hem blo keanem moni.

title: Sandlewood
text:
Sandlewood hemi wan lo valuable tri long <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a> we hem i makem big money igo long <a href="economi">economi</a> blo countri, sandlewood hemi wan tri we hem i unique aut long ol evri tri long Vanuatu. 
<a href="Frut">Frut</a> blo hem i smol mo i raun mo hem i luk black,size blong hem i luk smal olsem napanka or panian tree long english toktok . 
Hem i gat braun stampa mo grin lif,lif blong hem i luk smalsmal olsem naus.oli makem samting aut long hem olsem:Oil,perfume,soap mo fulap mo samting long hem. 
Everi bodi blong hem oli kat uses,studi i sowem se North Tanna hemi wan long island long Vanuatu i stap lead long sandlewood after long eromango .

title: Pandanas
text:
Pandanas (<a href="toktok%20Latin">toktok Latin</a>: Pandanus), hemi wan <a href="genus">genus</a> blong tri long famli blong "<a href="Pandanaceae">Pandanaceae</a>". Hemi gat <a href="frut%20blong%20pandanas">frut blong pandanas</a> we pipol likem kakae, mo lef blong hemi oli save wivim mat long hem.
Hem i gat mo o les 746 <a href="species">species</a> blong pandanas, foeksampol "<a href="Pandanus%20tectorius">Pandanus tectorius</a>", "<a href="Pandanus%20fascicularis">Pandanus fascicularis</a>", "<a href="Pandanus%20utilis">Pandanus utilis</a>", "<a href="Pandanus%20julianettii">Pandanus julianettii</a>" ('karuka'), etc., pipol i save kakae frut blong olgeta disfala pandanas o sam narafala pandanas.
Frut blong hem i hung antap olsem wan 'raon bol', sipos yu wantem kakae yu mas katem 'raon bol' ia.
linked_text: Pandanas (toktok Latin: Pandanus), hemi wan genus blong tri long famli blong "Pandanaceae". Hem i gat mo o les 746 species blong pandanas, foeksampol "Pandanus tectorius", "Pandanus fascicularis", "Pandanus utilis", "Pandanus julianettii" ('karuka'), etc., pipol i save kakae frut blong olgeta disfala pandanas o sam narafala pandanas. Frut blong hem i hung antap olsem wan 'raon bol', sipos yu wantem kakae yu mas katem 'raon bol' ia.

title: Envaeromen
text: Envaeromen hemi wan ples blong ol bigfala <a href="tri">tri</a> mo bigfala leaf mo ol <a href="pijin">pijin</a> wetem ol narafala anemol long forest. Envaeromen <a href="solwota">solwota</a> blong hemi ol <a href="fis">fis</a> , shell,<a href="koral">koral</a> ref, seawed, mo ol narafala wan long solwota mo sanbis . Nao envaeromen hemi blong blokem yumi long ol greenhaos gas be hemi i givim oxygen blong tekem mo tekem carbondioxde mo long solwota hemi givem yumi meat o solwota blong swim so envaeromen hemi importen tumas long yumi ol man.

title: Ekonomi
text: Sandlewood hemi helpem bigwan ekonomi blong kauntri, Tanna hem wan we i stap benefit bigwan long sandlewood inside long wanwan hausehol. yu save lukim tu kilo i ingris iko long eight thousand vatu long wan kilo long ia 2015. Itch haushold oli makem money long itch competative buyer, ol main benefit blo tri ia sandlewood : money long itch hausholder, development olsem community project mo fulap mo samting we i save helpem ol holder we oli <a href="doom">doom</a> i stap.

title: Nakamal
text: Nakamal hem i wan ples wei ol man mo woman oli ko drink kava lo hem, Mo tu lo nakamal ol servem ol kava lo shel blo kokonat. Nakamal tu hem i wan ples yu ol woman i no save ko lo hem sam fala aelan custom mo believe blo olgeta se ol woman oli no allow blo ko lo nakamal blo drink kava. Mo tu nakamal hem wan import house tu from round lo ol aelan blo Port Vila, Nakamal hem olsem wan court house blo ol community lo village o ples blo meting blo community lo wan village.

title: Donald Trump
text:
Donald John Trump (boe 14 Jun 1946) i hed blong stet blong <a href="Yunaeted%20Stet%20blong%20Amerika">Yunaeted Stet blong Amerika</a>.
Feswan, Trump hem wan bisnisman, mo wan man blong TV program. 
Long novemba 2016, ol man US oli elektem hem presiden blong USA blong 4 yias (2016-2020). Hemi saed wetem <a href="Republican%20Party%20blong%20USA">Republican Party</a>.
Long novemba 2020 hem i wantem presiden bakegen, be hemi lusum eleksen: <a href="Joe%20Biden">Joe Biden</a> nao ikam presiden.

title: Langwis
text:
Langwis i fasin blong talem ol samting. Ol kaen langwis i kat strakja long hem. I kat fulap langwis lo <a href="wol">wol</a>. Long <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a> oli toktok long bitim 100 langwis blong ples.
Sapos tufala man toktok tufala langwis we oli no semak, bae tufala i no haremsave toktok blong narawan. Be i no isi blong talem stret se langwis i wan o tu. Wan langwis olsemia nem blong hem, langwis jen.
Langwis long bren.
Man we oli save moa langwis, bren blong hem i save moa helti.
Saon blong toktok.
I kat langwis blong toktok, mo langwis wetem han, mo nara kaen langwis, be toktok i faswan.
Ol man yusum <a href="maot">maot</a>, <a href="nos">nos</a>, <a href="voes">voes</a> mo <a href="lang">lang</a> blong mekem ol saon blong toktok.
linked_text: Langwis i fasin blong talem ol samting. Ol kaen langwis i kat strakja long hem. I kat fulap langwis lo [[wol]]. Long [[Vanuatu]] oli toktok long bitim 100 langwis blong ples. Sapos tufala man toktok tufala langwis we oli no semak, bae tufala i no haremsave toktok blong narawan. Be i no isi blong talem stret se langwis i wan o tu. Wan langwis olsemia nem blong hem, langwis jen. Langwis long bren. [[Man]] we oli save moa langwis, bren blong hem i save moa helti. Saon blong toktok. I kat langwis blong toktok, mo langwis wetem han, mo nara kaen langwis, be toktok i faswan. Ol man yusum maot, nos, voes mo lang blong mekem ol saon blong toktok.

title: Joe Biden
text:
Joe Biden (fulnem "Joseph Robinette Biden Jr."), bon 1942, i politikis blong <a href="Yunaeted%20Stet%20blong%20Amerika">Yunaeted Stet blong Amerika</a>. 
Long yias 2008-2016, Biden hem vaespresiden blong presiden <a href="Barack%20Obama">Barack Obama</a>, olsem nambatu jif blong kantri.
Go-go, ale long novemba 2020, Biden hemi bitim presiden <a href="Donald%20Trump">Donald Trump</a> long eleksen: hemi kasem 81 milion balots, wan rekod namba long histri blo kantri ia. Olsemia, hem kam presiden blong USA blong 4 yias (2020-2024), wetem vaespresiden blong hem <a href="Kamala%20Harris">Kamala Harris</a>.

title: Marie Curie

title: Namba (Buk blong Baebol)
text:

Hem i talem stori blong Israel, ol pipol blong God, taem God i sevem olgeta from Ijip mo i sta tekem olgeta i go long gudfala ples, be olgeta i no stap trastem hem mo oli stap long taem long deset fromwe oli no trastem God.

title: Aien
text:
Aien, o aean, em i bin wan <a href="Elemen%20blong%20Kemistri">elemen</a> blong <a href="Kemistri">Kemistri</a>. Em i staka kapa blong nambatu blong wol. Simbol blong em Fe. Em i bin wan kaen metal. Aien i save kombaenem long <a href="okisijen">okisijen</a> blong air blong mekem rust.
Aien blong Indastri.
Pipol ol i save yusum aien blong mekem plante kaen masin, baiskel, trak. Pipol ol i save mekem plante kaen tools blong aien.
Aien mo carbon ol i mekem steel; steel i strong i bitim aien.
Aien blong Niutrisen.
Aien em i wan empoten pat blong helti kaekae. Yelo pat blong ol ek ol i gat plante aien insaed, mo ol fis mo jiken ol i gat fulap aien insaed.

Yelo [[pat]] blong ol ek ol i gat plante aien insaed, mo ol fis mo jiken ol i gat fulap aien insaed.

title: Aiodin
text:
Aiodin (Iodine) em i wan elemen blong <a href="kemistri">kemistri</a>. Simbol blong em i I; namba blong atom blong em i 53. Bernard Courtois, wan man blong kemistri blong <a href="Franis">Franis</a>, faenem fastaem aiodin long yia 1811.
Yusum sol we i gat aiodin insaed em i bin wan pat blong helti kaikai.
Long [[medisin]] pipol save yusum aiodin blong faetem o stopem infeksen.

title: Araki (lanwis)
text:
Araki (lokol nem "Raki") hem wan lanwis blong <a href="Vanuatu">Vanuatu</a>. Stamba ples blong hem, aelan blong <a href="Araki%20aelan">Araki</a> we i stap long saot blong <a href="Santo">Santo</a> (<a href="Sanma">Sanma provens</a>).
Histri blong lanwis ia.
Olsem evri <a href="Lanwis%20blong%20Vanuatu">tokples blong Vanuatu</a>, Araki hem wan <a href="Oceanic%20lanwis">Oceanic lanwis</a>, memba blong bigfela <a href="Austronesian%20lanwis">Austronesian famle</a>.
Lanwis ia tedei.
Tedei ia, ol lingwis i talem se lanwis blong Araki, igat 8 man nomo i stap yet we i save tok long hem.

title: Jane Elizabeth Manning James
text:
Jane Elizabeth Manning (samples long 1822–1908) i bin wan long ol faef pikinini we oli bon insaed long famli blong wan fri Afrika- Amerika kapol long Konektikat, long wan taem we plante long ol blak pipol insaed long Yunaeted Stet, oli bin stap olsem ol slef.1 Olsem wan yang adalt, hem i bin joenem Niu Kanan Kongregesen Jos long 1841, be 18 manis afta, long Winta blong yia 1842–43, wetem samfala memba blong famli blong hem, mo hem, oli bin baptaes insaed long Jos Ia blong Jisas Kraes blong Ol Lata-dei Sent. I no longtaem afta, Jane wetem ol narawan insaed long famli blong hem, oli bin wantem joenem Ol Sent long Nauvu, mekem se oli aot long Konektikat, mo travel i go long Niu Yok, mo oli bin plan blong travel long ol stim bot mo ol kanal bot. Be, oli no bin letem olgeta long sip from se oli bin blak, mekem se oli mas wokbaot long kolosap 1288 kilometa ia we i stap. Long Peoria, Ilinoa, ol lokol atoriti oli bin askem kwestin long Famli Mannings, se oli ol slef we oli ronwe o no, mo oli bin askem ol pepawok blong olgeta blong pruvum se oli fri. Fasin blong agensem man from kala blong skin, i bin wan samting we bae i kam blokem Jane long ful laef blong hem.
Taem hem i bin kasem Nauvu, kwiktaem Jane i kam fren wetem Josef mo Ema Smit. Hem i bin laef wetem tufala mo i bin wok insaed long haos blong tufala. Long wan taem, Ema i bin invaetem Jane blong i akseptem se bae oli adoptem hem olsem wan pikinini, i kam insaed long Smit famli, mo hemia tru long wan prishud siling.2 Jane i no bin akseptem, hemia from hem i no bin andastanem niufala praktis ia, be hem i bin biliv strong long rol blong Josef olsem wan profet. Samtaem afta, hem i bin talem: “Mi bin save Profet Josef. Hem i wan man we i stret mo i gud tumas; i no gat wan narawan we mi bin luk we i olsem long wol ia. … Mi save stret se hem i bin wan profet, from se mi save hemia.”3
Tru long ol storian wetem Josef mo wetem mama blong hem, Lusi Mak Smit, Jane i bin lanem moa abaot Buk blong Momon mo translesen wok blong hem, mo i kam blong andastanem mo respektem ol odinens blong tempol.
Jane i bin maredem Isaac James, wan blak konvet we i gat fri laef, mo hem i blong Niu Jesi. Tufala, wetem boe blong Jane, Sylvester, oli bin aot long Nauvu long 1846 oli go long Wes wetem Ol Sent. Long manis Jun long yia ia, boe blong Jane mo Isaac, Silas, i bon i kam long wol ia. Long nekis yia blong hem, famli ia i bin krosem ol flat ples, mo oli kasem Sol Lek Vale long samples Septemba blong yia 1847. Isaac mo Jane, tufala i gat sikis moa pikinini, mo tu (2) long olgeta nomo i bin laef i longwan i bitim Jane. Semmak olsem ol narawan we oli bin kam stap long Sol Lek Vale, Jane mo Isaac i bin wok had blong lukluk long famli blong tufala. Isaac i bin wok olsem wan wokman, mo wanwan taem, i draevem hankat blong Brigham Yang, mo Jane i bin stap wivim ol klos, i mekem ol klos, mo i wasem klos, olsem we hem i bin mekem long Nauvu.
Raorao blong tufala i bin mekem se Isaac mo Jane i divos long 1870. Afta long hemia, Jane i bin mared sot taem wetem wan foma slef, Frank Perkins, be i no longtaem afta, i gohed blong stap olsem wan singgel mama mo bubuwoman. Nid long saed blong mane mo ded blong ol trifala pikinini blong hem i mekem se Jane i gobak wok. Hem i bin mekem mo salem sop, mo tufala nara boe blong hem oli wok olsem ol wokman. Long 1890, afta we hem i bin stap longwe blong 20 yia, Isaac i kambak long Sol Lek Siti, i kambak long Jos, mo i gat wan gudfala rilesensip wetem Jane. Taem hem i ded wan yia afta, oli bin holem fenerol seves blong Isaac long hom blong Jane.
Truaot long ol hadtaem blong laef blong hem, Jane i gohed blong komitim hem long fet blong hem long ol tijing blong gospel, mo i tekem se membasip blong hem insaed long Jos, i impoten tumas. Hem i mekem ol donesen i go long wok blong bildim tempol, mo i bin tekpat long Rilif Sosaeti mo Young Ladies’ Retrenchment Sosaeti (Sosaeti blong Ol Woman we Oli Sapotem Wok blong Laef Simpol).4 Jane i bin gat janis blong gat fulap eksperiens wetem ol presen blong Spirit, mo hem i bin gat ol visen, ol drim, ol hiling tru long fet, mo i toktok ol lanwis. Samtaem afta long laef blong hem, hem i bin raetem: “Fet blong mi long Gospel blong Jisas Kraes, i strong nomo i stap tedei. No. Sapos i posibol, ating i moa strong bitim dei ia we mi bin baptaes.”5
Bitwin 1884 mo 1904, Jane i bin stap toktok o raet oltaem i go long ol lida blong Jos—Jon Teila, Wilfod Wudrof, Sina D. H. Yang, mo Josef F. Smit— mo i bin askem raet blong hem i kasem tempol endaomen blong hem, mo blong hem i save sil.6 Long tetaem ia, ol blak man mo woman we oli ol Lata-dei Sent, oli no bin gat raet blong tekpat long plante long ol odinens blong tempol. Long 1888, stek presiden Angus M. Cannon i bin givim raet long Jane blong hem i mekem ol baptaes blong ol famli blong hem we oli bin ded finis.7 Long en, ol lida blong Jos oli bin letem hem blong hem i sil, tru long proksi wok, blong hem i joenem famli blong Josef Smit, taem we hem i bin wan wokman blong olgeta long 1894, we i wan samting we i bin hapen wan taem ia nomo. I nomata se hem i no bin kasem tempol endaomen o famli siling long taem we hem i bin laef, ol odinens ia, oli bin mekem long bihaf blong hem long 1979.8
Hem i bin ded long 16 Epril 1908, taem hem i bin gat 95 yia, mo i bin oltaem wan fetful Lata-dei Sent. Deseret News i givim ripot se: “I gat samfala pipol we oli bin luksave olgeta se oli gat moa fet mo oli moa fetful bitim Jane Manning James; mo nomata se hem i wan simpol woman, namba blong ol fren mo ol pipol we hem i save olgeta, i bitim ol handred.”
linked_text: Jane Elizabeth Manning (samples long 1822–1908) i bin wan long ol [[faef]] pikinini we oli bon insaed long famli blong wan fri [[Afrika-]] [[Amerika]] kapol long Konektikat, long wan taem we plante long ol blak pipol insaed long [[Yunaeted Stet]], oli bin stap olsem ol slef.1 Olsem wan yang adalt, hem i bin joenem [[Niu]] Kanan Kongregesen Jos long 1841, be 18 manis afta, long Winta blong yia 1842–43, wetem samfala memba blong famli blong hem, mo hem, oli bin baptaes insaed long Jos Ia blong [[Jisas Kraes]] blong Ol Lata-dei Sent. I no longtaem afta, Jane wetem ol narawan insaed long famli blong hem, oli bin wantem joenem Ol Sent long Nauvu, mekem se oli aot long Konektikat, mo travel i go long [[Niu]] Yok, mo oli bin plan blong travel long ol stim bot mo ol kanal bot. Be, [[oli]] no bin letem olgeta long sip from se [[oli]] bin blak, mekem se [[oli]] mas wokbaot long kolosap 1288 kilometa ia we i stap. Long Peoria, Ilinoa, ol lokol atoriti [[oli]] bin askem kwestin long Famli Mannings, se [[oli]] ol slef we [[oli]] ronwe o no, mo [[oli]] bin askem ol pepawok blong olgeta blong pruvum se [[oli]] fri. Fasin blong agensem man from kala blong skin, i bin wan samting we bae i kam blokem Jane long ful laef blong hem. Taem hem i bin kasem Nauvu, kwiktaem Jane i kam fren wetem Josef mo Ema Smit. Hem i bin laef wetem tufala mo i bin wok insaed long haos blong tufala. Long wan taem, Ema i bin invaetem Jane blong i akseptem se bae oli adoptem hem olsem wan pikinini, i kam insaed long Smit famli, mo hemia tru long wan prishud siling.2 Jane i no bin akseptem, hemia from hem i no bin andastanem niufala praktis ia, be hem i bin biliv strong long rol blong Josef olsem wan profet. Samtaem afta, hem i bin talem: “[[Mi]] bin [[save]] Profet Josef. Hem i wan man we i stret mo i [[gud]] tumas; i no gat wan narawan we mi bin luk we i olsem long [[wol]] ia. … [[Mi]] save stret se hem i bin wan profet, from se mi save hemia.”3 Tru long ol storian wetem Josef mo wetem mama blong hem, Lusi Mak Smit, Jane i bin lanem moa abaot Buk blong Momon mo translesen wok blong hem, mo i kam blong andastanem mo respektem ol odinens blong tempol. Jane i bin maredem Isaac James, wan blak konvet we i gat fri laef, mo hem i blong [[Niu]] Jesi. Tufala, wetem boe blong Jane, Sylvester, oli bin aot long Nauvu long 1846 oli go long Wes wetem Ol Sent. Long manis Jun long yia ia, boe blong Jane mo Isaac, Silas, i bon i [[kam]] long [[wol]] ia. Long nekis yia blong hem, famli ia i bin krosem ol flat ples, mo oli kasem [[Sol]] Lek Vale long samples Septemba blong yia 1847. Isaac mo Jane, tufala i gat sikis moa pikinini, mo tu (2) long olgeta nomo i bin laef i longwan i bitim Jane. Semmak olsem ol narawan we oli bin [[kam]] stap long [[Sol]] Lek [[Vale]], Jane mo Isaac i bin wok had blong lukluk long famli blong tufala. Isaac i bin wok olsem wan wokman, mo wanwan taem, i draevem hankat blong Brigham Yang, mo Jane i bin stap wivim ol klos, i mekem ol klos, mo i wasem klos, olsem we hem i bin mekem long Nauvu. Raorao blong tufala i bin mekem se Isaac mo Jane i divos long 1870. Afta long hemia, Jane i bin mared sot taem wetem wan foma slef, Frank Perkins, be i no longtaem afta, i gohed blong stap olsem wan singgel mama mo bubuwoman. Nid long saed blong mane mo ded blong ol trifala pikinini blong hem i mekem se Jane i gobak wok. Hem i bin mekem mo salem sop, mo tufala nara boe blong hem oli wok olsem ol wokman. Long 1890, afta we hem i bin stap longwe blong 20 yia, Isaac i kambak long [[Sol Lek Siti]], i kambak long Jos, mo i gat wan gudfala rilesensip wetem Jane. Taem hem i ded wan yia afta, oli bin holem fenerol seves blong Isaac long hom blong Jane. Truaot long ol hadtaem blong laef blong hem, Jane i gohed blong komitim hem long fet blong hem long ol tijing blong gospel, mo i tekem se membasip blong hem insaed long Jos, i impoten tumas. Hem i mekem ol donesen i go long wok blong bildim tempol, mo i bin tekpat long Rilif Sosaeti mo Young Ladies’ Retrenchment Sosaeti (Sosaeti blong Ol Woman we Oli Sapotem Wok blong Laef Simpol).4 Jane i bin gat janis blong gat fulap eksperiens wetem ol presen blong Spirit, mo hem i bin gat ol visen, ol drim, ol hiling tru long fet, mo i toktok ol lanwis. Samtaem afta long laef blong hem, hem i bin raetem: “Fet blong mi long Gospel blong [[Jisas Kraes]], i strong nomo i stap tedei. No. Sapos i posibol, ating i moa strong bitim dei ia we mi bin baptaes.”5 Bitwin 1884 mo 1904, Jane i bin stap toktok o raet oltaem i go long ol lida blong Jos—Jon Teila, Wilfod Wudrof, [[Sina]] [[D. H.]] Yang, mo Josef [[F. Smit]]— mo i bin askem raet blong hem i kasem tempol endaomen blong hem, mo blong hem i save sil.6 Long tetaem ia, ol blak man mo woman we oli ol Lata-dei Sent, oli no bin gat raet blong tekpat long plante long ol odinens blong tempol. Long 1888, stek presiden [[Angus M. Cannon]] i bin givim raet long Jane blong hem i mekem ol baptaes blong ol famli blong hem we oli bin ded finis.7 Long en, ol lida blong Jos oli bin letem hem blong hem i sil, tru long proksi wok, blong hem i joenem famli blong [[Josef Smit]], taem we hem i bin wan wokman blong olgeta long 1894, we i wan samting we i bin hapen wan taem ia nomo. I nomata se hem i no bin kasem tempol endaomen o famli siling long taem we hem i bin laef, ol odinens ia, oli bin mekem long bihaf blong hem long 1979.8 Hem i bin ded long 16 Epril 1908, taem hem i bin gat 95 yia, mo i bin oltaem wan fetful Lata-dei Sent. [[Deseret News]] i givim ripot se: “I gat samfala pipol we [[oli]] bin luksave olgeta se [[oli]] gat moa fet mo [[oli]] moa fetful bitim Jane Manning James; mo nomata se hem i wan simpol woman, namba blong ol fren mo ol pipol we hem i save olgeta, i bitim ol handred.”

title: Kasakstan
text:
Kasakstan (kz. - "Қазақстан Республикасы") i kaontri long <a href="Esia">Esia</a>. I long <a href="Rusia">Rusia</a>, <a href="Jaena">Jaena</a>, <a href="Kirgistan">Kirgistan</a>, <a href="Asbekistan">Asbekistan</a>, <a href="Tukmenistan">Tukmenistan</a>. I blong hem i <a href="Nursultan">Nursultan</a>. Presidens blong hem i <a href="Kassym-Jomart%20Tokayev">Kassym-Jomart Tokayev</a>. Praem Minista blong hem i <a href="Askar%20Manin">Askar Manin</a>.
Long Julae 2017, populaesen blong Kasakstan i stap araon 18.5 milien.

title: Tyler Jacobs
text:
Tyler Grant Jacobs (bon long <a href="25%20Oktoba">25 Oktoba</a> <a href="1977">1977</a> long <a href="Yunaeted%20Stet%20blong%20Amerika">Yunaeted Stet blong Amerika</a>), em i wan krietiv daerekta, man blong <a href="grafik%20disaen">grafik disaen</a>, man blong miusik, <a href="bloga">bloga</a> mo foma <a href="pikinini%20akta">pikinini akta</a> blong Yunaeted Stet blong Amerika.
Em i bin foma memba blong miusik grup <a href="GOGO13">GOGO13</a>. Tyler Jacobs i stap impoten wetem wok blong em olsem krietiv daerekta long TV show "<a href="Yo%20Gabba%20Gabba%21">Yo Gabba Gabba!</a>".
linked_text: Tyler Grant Jacobs (bon long 25 Oktoba 1977 long [[Yunaeted Stet blong Amerika]]), em i wan krietiv daerekta, man blong grafik disaen, man blong miusik, bloga mo foma pikinini akta blong Yunaeted Stet blong Amerika. Em i bin foma memba blong miusik grup GOGO13. Tyler Jacobs i stap impoten wetem wok blong em olsem krietiv daerekta long TV show "Yo Gabba Gabba!".

title: Fas Visen
text:
<a href="Josef%20Smit">Josef Smit</a> i pablisim tufala stori abaot Fas Visen long taem we hem i bin laef yet. Faswan long olgeta ia, we tedei yumi save olsem Josef Smit—Histri, oli bin putum insaed long Perel we I Gat Bigfala Praes, mo olsem ia nao hem i kam stori ia we oli save gud long hem. Tufala nara stori, we oli no bin pablisim, be oli bin raetem long ol fasfala laef stori blong Josef Smit, mo afta long hemia, hem i bin raetem long wan jenol, plante taem, oli fogetem, kasem taem we ol man blong raetem histri, we oli wok blong Jos Ia blong Jisas Kraes Ia blong Ol Lata-dei Sent oli faenem ol stori ia bakegen mo oli pablisim olgeta long ol yia 1960. Stat long tetaem ia, olgeta pepa ia, oli bin toktok raon long olgeta plante taem long ol magasin blong Jos, long ol wok we Jos i printim, o, olgeta we oli wok wetem Jos oli printim, mo tu, ol Lata-dei Sent pipol we oli stap stadi oli bin pablisim long ol nara ples. Antap long ol stori we hemwan i bin raetemdaon, i gat narafala faef stori blong visen blong Josef Smit we samfala pipol we oli bin laef long sem taem olsem hem, oli bin raetem.
Ol defren stori abaot Fas Visen ia, oli tokbaot wan semfala stori nomo, be samfala ditel mo samting we oli tokbaot plante nao i defren smol long ol narawan. Ol man we oli stap raetem histri, oli save se taem wan man i stap talem bakegen mo bakegen wan eksperiens blong hem long ol defren ples, mo long ol defren pipol ova long plante yia, bae wanwan stori ia bae i tokbaot bigwan sam defren pat blong eksperiens ia, mo bae i gat ol spesel ditel we i no stap long sam narafala ples. I tru. Ol samting olsem we oli defren long ol stori ia blong Fas Visen, oli stap long ol defren skripja stori blong visen blong Pol long rod i go long Damaskes, mo long eksperiens blong Ol Aposol antap long Hil ia we Jisas I Kam Niu I Kam Narafala. Be yet, i nomata ol samting ia we oli defren, wan semfala stori i stap long evriwan long ol stori ia abaot Fas Visen. Sam oli mekem mistek mo oli toktok bigwan se eni samting we i defren taem oli stap talem bakegen stori ia, i wan pruf se hemia i wan giaman stori. Be i no olsem. Ol rij rekod blong histri oli mekem se yumi save lanem moa abaot bigfala taem ia, i bitim we sapos oli neva bin raetemdaon.

title: San
text:
San (simbol: ) i wan <a href="sta">sta</a> long senta blong <a href="Sistem%20blong%20San">Sistem blong San</a> long Galaksi blong yumi. <a href="Et">Et</a>, plenet blong yumi, mo ol nafala plenet oli stap revolvem araon San. Hem i nambawan sos blong hotsan mo <a href="enaji">enaji</a> blong laef long Et.
San i waet sta. Sipos komperem long narafala sta, San i no tumas big. Be sta ia i tumas wom mo hevi.
